---
import PushableButton from '~/components/PushableButton.astro'
import Layout from '~/layouts/base.astro'
---

<Layout title="About me">
	<h1 class="pb-6 pt-12 text-5xl font-extrabold">About me</h1>
	<ul
		class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-white text-lg font-medium flex flex-col space-y-3 mb-12"
	>
		<li>
			🌊 Originally from Barcelona, Spain, I'm now living in Copenhagen,
			Denmark.
		</li>
		<li>💻 I began my journey as a full-time developer in 2021.</li>
		<li>
			👷‍♂️ My background is in electrical engineering, with previous experience in
			the PV solar industry.
		</li>
		<li>
			🎮 I'm passionate about playing and collecting video games, and I'm
			currently expanding my GameBoy collection—my favorite childhood handheld!
		</li>
		<li>
			📚 I have a deep interest in the history of game development. One of my
			all-time favorite books is Masters of Doom, a truly inspirational story.
		</li>
		<li>⌚️ I'm a collector of retro Casio and G-Shock watches.</li>
	</ul>

	<div class="flex justify-center w-full pb-3">
		<PushableButton
			as="a"
			href="https://vgmestre-cv.netlify.app/"
			target="_blank"
			rel="noopener noreferrer"
		>
			See my CV!
		</PushableButton>
	</div>
</Layout>
